		<div class="cont">
			<h2 id="games" class="game-text">Featured games</h2>
			<div class="row boom-boom">
				<div class="card col s12 m6 l4">
					<div class="card-image">
						<img
							src="https://vistapointe.net/images/pong-wallpaper-11.jpg"
						/>
						<span class="card-title">Pong Game</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-content">
						<p class="white-para">
							Pong is a two-dimensional sports game that simulates table
							tennis. The player controls a paddle in the game by tilting
							the mobile device.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card-action">
						<a class="btn btn--white sg" href="#">Start Game</a>
						<a class="btn btn--white cr" href="#">Connect Room</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card col s12 m6 l4">
					<div class="card-image">
						<img
							src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EnFsmJU_78g/Uaq-HpBW8WI/AAAAAAAABhI/NiWtcvth7XM/s1600/Atari+breakout+game+wallpaper.gif"
						/>
						<span class="card-title">Atari Breakout</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-content">
						<p class="white-para">
							Breakout is an arcade game where there is a layer of bricks
							and the goal is to destroy them all by repeatedly bouncing
							a ball off a paddle into them.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card-action">
						<a class="btn btn--white sg" href="#">Start Game</a>
						<a class="btn btn--white cr" href="#">Connect Room</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="card col s12 m6 l4">
					<div class="card-image">
						<img src="../landing/img/car dash.png" />
						<span class="card-title">Car Dash</span>
					</div>
					<div class="card-content">
						<p class="white-para">
							Car Dash is a 3D game where you have to drive without
							beating the other car or truck. Difficulty will be
							increasing as you play.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card-action">
						<a class="btn btn--white sg" href="#">Start Game</a>
						<a class="btn btn--white cr" href="#">Connect Room</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
